text: Joseph Kim Mitchell (born July 10, 1952) is a Canadian guitarist. Mitchell was the singer and guitarist for the band Max Webster and now hosts a radio show for CILQ-FM (Q107) in Toronto. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian guitarists Category:Canadian radio personalities Category:Canadian rock musicians Category:Musicians from Ontario Category:People from Sarnia
